{"tid":2233192,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前線巴成難民｜加拿大開始接受香港民主派難民身份 首對抗爭夫婦獲批「公約難民」資格","createTime":"2020-10-07T02:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T07:33:40.000Z","uid":44209,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e364dfbfdc25e7dccdd849c7cd3054618862daff","tid":2233192,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"前線巴成難民｜加拿大開始接受香港民主派難民身份 首對抗爭夫婦獲批「公約難民」資格<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果日報】國際社會深切關注「港版國安法」侵蝕香港人權，加拿大《環球郵報》（The Globe and Mail）報道指，加拿大加入英國之列，接納香港抗爭者及民主人士以難民身份申請加拿大的庇護，已有首對抗爭夫婦獲批「公約難民」資格。報道指，加拿大移民和難民局（Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada）在今年9月1日以書信形式，通知一對30多歲的港人夫婦接納他們的庇護申請，並將定義他們為公約難民（Convention refugees）。據悉，二人都是去年反修例運動的活躍份子，該名33歲男子更是前線抗爭者兼本地政黨人士，還「營運一間倉庫為抗爭者製作和提供防具」。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20201007新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201007/DGZWC7KJUNCFZNHIBTQSQ2FPFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201007%2FDGZWC7KJUNCFZNHIBTQSQ2FPFY%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=780ae4db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201007%2FDGZWC7KJUNCFZNHIBTQSQ2FPFY%2F&h=fc4e4df6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201007/DGZWC7KJUNCFZNHIBTQSQ2FPFY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4020&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=11eb51bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4020</a>"},{"pid":"a0183b917ef29e5b4b28747ab345c6c2d657fa65","tid":2233192,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:14:06.000Z","msg":"希望手足響加拿大生活快樂"},{"pid":"20d317660c4f831e84fe0649c6ce91476db5898e","tid":2233192,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\"