"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"同佢地買左唔少裝<br />\n各位心照"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:28:36.000Z","msg":"前熱狗？"},{"pid":"eaf062fc38d7784f827fad8c0830418ebe0384ba","tid":2233192,"uid":82394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望你哋喺果邊順利展開新生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b502eaa301ea7f14d9c9e59939352dc588e4df","tid":2233192,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd967587214d842d9a80dafaaef59882015c8953","tid":2233192,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3b7129854897224b3fdbc621580481ddec9305","tid":2233192,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;李政熙（英語：Keita LEE Ching-hei），香港政治人物，為大圍村原居民，已婚，育有一子一女，曾任職煤氣安裝技工，政治組織熱血公民前成員，2017年脫離該組織。2019年8月起經營名為「國難五金」的店鋪，在反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動發生時期及之後，在各個遊行或示威熱點附近，以日租或短期形式租鋪，開設售賣店售賣防毒面具、頭盔、眼罩、口罩及手套等防護裝備，「國難五金」首次在2019年8月3日於旺角道開業，首次營業賣出約四百多套裝備。[1][2]現時店鋪銷售主要在大埔區，在冠狀病毒影響香港期間，國難五金兼售防疫用品。其弟李珏熙亦為熱血公民前成員。[3] &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Keita LEE Ching-hei<br />\n李政熙<br />\n個人資料<br />\n性別 男<br />\n出生 1986年（33－34歲）<br />\n 英屬香港<br />\n國籍 香港 中國（香港）&rdquo;<br />\n居住地  香港<br />\n網站 李政熙的Facebook專頁"},{"pid":"f8fc580e404bf04be5252578ad34bc5848d6f641","tid":2233192,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"識玩cap完水就走，去加拿大安享晚年，D仔女又接受外國優質教育"},{"pid":"79c7971e0b9f5665c8f44f4198dfb45b498b47b8","tid":2233192,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8fc580e404bf04be5252578ad34bc5848d6f641","tid":2233192,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"識玩cap完水就走，去加拿大安享晚年，D仔女又接受外國優質教育"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"你個post 係咪開比你自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔走比港共迫害, 係咪你幫手頂罪?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冷嘲熱諷係冇意思，現實一樣係咁衰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024979</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0915/20190915090118363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0915%2F20190915090118363.jpg&h=9d2d70ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本在西營盤開鋪營業，售賣防毒面具等裝備的「國難五金」，宣佈在深水埗開設「旗艦店」，惟今日開張不久即被警方「掃場」，多名警員帶同法庭搜查令搜查店鋪，搜索近兩小時後離開，無帶走任何貨品。"},{"pid":"a204699df369474c8140892ad7e4ebda388d114c","tid":2233192,"uid":249708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"我有唔少食黃店既前線打卡相<br />\n可申請？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}